metadata.name: Sismo DAO - Gen[0] Ziki Membership
metadata.description: With a maximum supply of 500, this membership NFT has been handed out to the very first generation (Gen[0]) of individuals who joined the Sismo DAO. It could only be minted by the pioneers of the Sismo community who expressed interest in its early days. This collection admin keys were burned. This NFT enables its holders to access the the Sismo DAO Discord, become official Zikies and prove they belong to Gen[0].
